name: Unisex Bathrooms
directions:
Throught the front door on the first floor, follow the hallway and its on the lefthand side before the elevators. 
Second floor bathroom (button three in the elevator) right off the elevator, the hallway to the right is also unisex.
Those are the two that I have come across, though it is a doctor's office in a fairly large building, they most likely have more than these two bathrooms.
comment: This doctor's office has always had, from my expierience, very kind staff and are very LGBTQ+ friendly. If you can't get the first floor bathroom because its occupied a staff member could direct you, usually, without any problem.
